'''Engineering''' is the practical application of [[science]]. This is accomplished through [[knowledge]], [[mathematics]], and practical [[experience]] applied to the [[design]] of useful [[object (philosophy)|object]]s or [[Process (engineering)|processes]].  Professional practitioners of engineering are called [[engineer]]s.

